{"tid":1862254,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你班連登仔 淨係識叫醫護罷工 個香港你地都有份架","createTime":"2020-02-04T14:01:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T16:34:44.000Z","uid":229751,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a1434c31412cb700316a8b965a9c15a716b6bd33","tid":1862254,"uid":229751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T14:01:46.000Z","msg":"連醫護咁難罷工既職業都可以罷到工<br />\n各行各業既大家 點解唔可以一齊罷工去幫醫護<br />\n因為醫護既罷工時間真係好有限 <br />\n一個星期既決戰時間 政府一早知道 所以一拖再拖<br />\n一星期後 醫護人員被迫復工 <br />\n政府繼續中門大開<br />\n<br />\n況且封關愈早愈好 一個星期已經可以比唔少病病者入左香港<br />\n<br />\n大家要係最短時間入面俾最大既壓力政府 先有可能迫到佢封關<br />\n<br />\n當然 條7婆都可以無視 <br />\n <br />\n但我地唔可以咩都唔做"},{"pid":"67315df35068a35feb26f6face6b990d953010a5","tid":1862254,"uid":208722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T14:06:11.000Z","msg":"推呢個<br />\n<br />\n支港共最怕全港大罷工"},{"pid":"a5cde8bd5c0364d9c06bd6eb5bc0f422127319a3","tid":1862254,"uid":220985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T14:06:44.000Z","msg":"pish 呢個！"},{"pid":"6e9914f53c9afdeae89cb88c0bab65026fc2e821","tid":1862254,"uid":140802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T14:11:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce8aa8ff5fc62b7907ef12ee48b99e23405f5a33","tid":1862254,"uid":44951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T14:14:48.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n個個話支持醫護罷工 第二日訓醒就繼續返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c82ca17232b3ffe519b4a017559469b16b41e81c","tid":1862254,"uid":223208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T14:16:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f779dd7ef3d43319b48ceb2ac6ca4a0c93f59a1f","tid":1862254,"uid":215876,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T14:17:24.000Z","msg":"突然間大量p牌同五毛狗+真心膠係度帶風嘅<br />\n表示而家爆發左就封關都無用<br />\n叫醫護復工<br />\n<b